summary: Peruvian living in the Netherlands. Graduated Summa cum laude for my Master’s Degree in Economics with specialization in Finance. Native Spanish speaker with English and Korean Proficiency and learning the Dutch language. International sales experience working as Sales Engineer at Yokogawa Netherlands. Proactive and performance oriented person, who is capable to create solutions in a constant changing environment and loves working together with others.
